      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta biji tu iṣgresnota ar\nSelta un Sudraba/ nn tawas\nDrehbes bija dahrgs Audektis/\nun Sihde/ nn iṣrakstihts Darbs.\nTu ehdi Kweeschus un Meddu\nun Etji/ nn tu biji tohti skaista/\nun tew iṣdewahs labbi/ kad tu\npar Walstibn tappi."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir weena Slawa no tew\niṣplande starp teem Paganeem\ntawa Skaistuma deht/ jo tas\nbija pilnigs zaur to Glihtumu/\nko es pee tew biju lizzis/ fakka\ntas Klungs KUNGS."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tu efi paḣahwifkees\nus tawu Skaistunu/ un tawas\nSlawas deht Mauzibu dsinnu-\nsi/ ir tu efi tawu Mauzibu iṣ-\nlaidusi/ wiṣaim kas fezzen pa-\ngabje/ irr winza peederrejti."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tu efi no tawahn\nDrehbehn zehmuﬁ/ un raibus\nAugstums preeſch tewim dar-\nrijti/ un us teem efi tu Mauzi-\nbu dsinnusi/ itt ka tas wehl ne\nttr bijis nedś buhs."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu efi arridsan tohś\nRihkus tawa Jaukuma zehimu-\nft no manna Selta un uo man-\nna Sudraba/ ko es tew biju de-\nwis/ un tu efi preeſch tew Wih-\nru Gihtmus darrijst/ un ar teem\nefi tu Mauzibu dsinnuti."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tu zehmi tawas iṣ-\nrakstitas Drehbes/ un efi tohś\napfegguﬁ/ un efi mannu Etji\nun mannu Kwehpja-Sahli win-"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Uu mannu Maisi/ ko\ntew derwu/ Miltus un Etji\nMeddu/ ar ko es tewi bakro-\neﬁi tu arridsan winseem pre-\nschā zehluﬁ/ par taldn Sm-\nschu. Tas irr notizzis/ fakka t\nKlugs KUNGS."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "En eﬁi arridsan tan-\nDehkus un tawas Meitas /\ntu man eﬁi dsemdejﬁ/ zehmu-\nun tohś teem uppurejﬁ par B-\nribu/ itt ka tas wehl mas buh-\nka tu * Mauzibu dsinnusi.\n* Un tew bij arridsan wehl nokaut."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka tv eﬁi mannuś Be-\nnus kawuﬁ/ un tohś nodewi-\nun likkusi tohś preekich winne-\n(zaur ugguni) cet."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tomehr tu wiffās taw-\nNegantibās un tawā Mau-\nschana ne eﬁi peeminnejﬁ ta-\nDeenas tawas Jannibas/kad-\npikka un kalla biji / un famih-\njama tawās Affinis."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas irr arridsan notiz-\npelz wiffās tawas Blehdibe-\n(waj waj tew!) fakka tas Klun-\nKUNGS."
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu eﬁi preekich teivā-\nKalno-Altarus taijﬁsi/ un A-\nstumus ikkatrā Cela.\n* Eebr: Wall: Mauku-Kaktus."
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un us ikkatra Zetta Pre-\nschu eﬁi tu tawas Augstum-\nustaifﬁsi/ un tawu Skaistu-\nfagabniuﬁ/ tu eﬁi tawas Rah-\nisplehtuﬁ prett wiffeem/kas-\nzen pagabje/ un leelu Manz-\ndsinuﬁ."
    }
  ],
